# Windows Care Kit (WCK) — .gitignore
# PUBLIC repo. Order matters: security deny-list first.

## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## SECURITY DENY-LIST (never commit — disk images, keys, secrets)
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.vhd
*.vhdx
*.vmcx
*.pfx
*.p12
*.pgp
*.gpg
*.asc
*.jks
*.keystore
*.pem
*.key
*.kdbx
*.ovpn
*.mobileprovision
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
id_ecdsa*
id_dsa*
*.ppk
wallet.dat
.git-credentials
.netrc
.pypirc
.npmrc
.env
.env.*
auth.json
oauth_creds.json
cred_blob*
.claude.json
*password*
*recovery-code*

## Payload = personal user data (tool/payload separation). NEVER committed.
payload/
*.payload/

## Local maintainer notes backup (pre-format redundancy) — internal cross-project
## notes + harness config. PUBLIC repo → NEVER committed.
.claude-memory-backup/

## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## .NET build output
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
bin/
obj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
publish/
artifacts/
TestResults/

## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## IDE / Visual Studio / Rider
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo

## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## Orchestration runtime — NEVER committed (regenerated per session)
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.planning/
/STAGING/
.cx_dispatch/
.ax_dispatch/
.cx_dispatch_locks/

## graphify knowledge graph — local generated arch map (regenerated, not source)
graphify-out/
.graphify_*

## Internal-only handoff reports surfaced inside the tree
**/REPORT.md
**/MANUAL_TODO.md

## Stray orchestration files dropped at repo root
/CODEX_DONE*
/CODEX_TASK*
/AGY_DONE*
/AGY_TASK*

## Legacy PowerShell tool (kept locally, not shipped)
legacy/

## Raw app screenshots (contain real installed-app names = personal data) + generated decks
docs/screenshots/_capture/
/WindowsCareKit_*.pdf

## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## Internal dev/process docs — NOT shipped (curate clean public docs before release).
## Status trackers, security scan reports/briefs, PR status, and contracts that
## reference the internal multi-agent build process. Kept on disk; screenshots stay public.
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/docs/*.md
/docs/security/

## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
## OS cruft
## ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.tmp/
/_process/
